reviewText: Love the corny horror movies! Too bad it wasn't Jack Frost 1 and 2 but Ice Cream Man is good too.
Quirky double feature thats sure to please fans of B-Horror flicks
Im so happy I finally Ice Cream Man on DVD for an affordable price!

My fiancee has talked about this movie and how it was an awesome movie but he could never find it. I found it in Amazon in less then 2 minutes. Ordered it in 5 and got it a day and half later to surprise him. He loves it!!!!
I DID NOT CARE FOR THESE TWO MOVIES AT ALL. I WASN'T PLEASED WITH THEM. THE TWO DUMBEST MOVIES I HAVE EVER SEEN
I enjoyed it it was sick

Ice Cream Man is a very funny "scary" movie, if you're into watching movies that are suppose to be scary that are just plain hilarious then this one may be right for you! I did not watch Jack Frost 2 yet.
